      <strong>Summary</strong>
    </p>
    <p xmlns="" class="description">Alvin is a Maker, the first to be born
    in a century.Now a grown man and a journeyman smith, Alvin has
    returned to his family in the town of Vigor Church. He will
    share in their isolation, work as a blacksmith, and try to
    teach anyone who wishes to learn the knack of being a Maker.
    For Alvin has had a vision of the Crystal City he will build,
    and he knows that he cannot build it alone.But he has left
    behind in Hatrack River enemies as well as true friends. His
    ancient foe, the Unmaker, whose cruel whispers and deadly plots
    have threatened Alvinâ€™s life at every turn, has found new
    hands to do his work of destruction.At the publisher's request,
